{"tid":1430921,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱有個客話啲年輕人成日搞事好煩！！！","createTime":"2019-08-08T01:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T02:11:06.000Z","uid":216662,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe125b0e1e990b2ca96371f80ee8b02f137347d3","tid":1430921,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:00:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的～<br />\n<br />\n個客一嚟就係咁講搞咁耐好煩，阻住乜乜乜，維穩物物物，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔鍾意香港就走啦</span></span>嗰三幅屁。。。<br />\n<br />\n開頭都唔理佢鳩up費事又同客嘈，但佢無啦啦放段袁詠儀鬧人片，聽到袁詠儀話學校無理由教到啲學生同啲仔女咁嘅時候，我頂唔住打斷我個客。。。<br />\n<br />\n我話以你個思考模式咁袁詠儀個仔<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好去呢間學校讀書囉，到全香港嘅學校都有教通識佢又唔鍾意，咪去外國讀書囉，到全世界都有教香港史嘅話咪送再個仔去外星讀啦！！！引用返你唔鍾意咪走囉呢句説話！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽完佢呆咗幾分鐘之後塊面黑到不得了，好彩佢有電話響救返佢先話走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7f617a2782cc06b8215bce29f7a091ac1d84c6","tid":1430921,"uid":78253,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:04:24.000Z","msg":"大把呢啲on9,同埋條片都唔知真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ac5ababbdcfc5752f1bc4deef3a39446684645","tid":1430921,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454724f86cab0a5c21e3b481c011bfa81349ffb1","tid":1430921,"uid":216662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f7f617a2782cc06b8215bce29f7a091ac1d84c6","tid":1430921,"uid":78253,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:04:24.000Z","msg":"大把呢啲on9,同埋條片都唔知真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:10:08.000Z","msg":"我每朝返工都同自講唔好得失啲客，但每日都同客嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas